commit message:
Merge pull request #2 from M2ck/patch-1

Added french translation
fix locale settings  not working with back button
Changed NDK r10d to r10e and gcc 4.6 to gcc 4.9
Fixed DNS resolver for static builds

Merge pull request #5 from itmplog/master

chinese translation & back button not update locale issue

Fix for 32bit NDK (close #6)

Use BusyBox build tools:
```
git clone https://github.com/meefik/busybox.git
cd busybox/contrib
export ANDROID_NDK_ROOT='/home/vagrant/android-ndk/r10e'
./bb-build.sh intel static
```
Revert to dynamic build (problem with sed -i on ARM)
Create strings.xml translated to spanish language

Support building with NDK 11 and API 21+

bb-build.sh
Preprend additional config file

patches-1.24.1/zz-NDK-11-fixes.patch
Update for functions removed in NDK 11
fdprintf isn't a standard function, dprintf is the standard
issetugid removed as 'No NDK user on Android should be writing setuid programs'

patches-1.24.1/android_ndk_defconfig-sdk21
Disable applets that are incompatible
FLASHCP/FLASH_LOCK/FLASH_UNLOCK/NANDWRITE/NANDDUMP: MTD support removed
TIME: wait3(2) removed. Should be supported again with busybox 1.24.2 (needs testing)
MDEV/MICROCOM: __set_errno removed

References:
https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/c/95471/
